data.description: Come Home to Sheffield Glenn! This home truly has everything you’re looking for and a whole lot more. You feel at home the moment you walk in this spacious home. This home has an elegant exterior with stone accents, sits on a large half cul-de-sac lot and has a large 3 car garage.  As you enter the home you notice the high ceilings and get a feel of the spaciousness this home has to offer. To your left is a formal dining room or a den/office with laminate floors. To your right is a room that is perfect for guest with its own half bath and privacy. You'll love the large island kitchen that opens up to a breakfast area and the great room. This layout is perfect for entertaining family and friends.  The great room is spacious and has access to the large covered screened in lanai/outdoor kitchen that wraps around to the sparkling saltwater pool with a paver brick patio in a fenced backyard offering a peaceful vantage point.  Picture yourself dipping in your toes or soaking in the backyard pool built 2019. Situated in Sheffield Glenn which is a single entrance neighborhood. The community has a low HOA fee and NO CDD.  Sidewalks meander among residences and encourage a sense of community with a mutual respect for nature. It is about a half a mile to top-rated schools, Buffalo Creek Park (a dog friendly local park with baseball, soccer, and football fields plus hiking trails, playgrounds, and picnic pavilions), and nearby Buffalo Creek Golf Course. The location is close to shopping, dining, entertainment, I-75, and I-275 for commuting.
